{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a012", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 18, "line_end": 18, "verbatim": "This example Demographics dataset does not include all the DM required and expected variables, only those that illustrate the variables that represent arm information. The following example illustrates values of ARMCD for subjects in Example Trial 1, described in Section 7.2.1, Trial Arms. This study included 2 elements, screen and run-in, before subjects were randomized to treatment. For this study, the sponsor submitted data on all subjects, including screen-failure subjects.", "parent_section": "§DM.2 [Example 2]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["Section 7.2.1"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a013", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 20, "line_end": 20, "verbatim": "**Row 1:** Subject 001 was randomized to arm \"Drug A\". As shown in the SE dataset, this subject completed the \"Drug A\" element, so their actual arm was also \"Drug A\".", "parent_section": "§DM.2 [Example 2]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a014", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 22, "line_end": 22, "verbatim": "**Row 2:** Subject 002 was randomized to arm \"Drug B\". As shown in the SE dataset, their actual arm was consistent with their randomization.", "parent_section": "§DM.2 [Example 2]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a015", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 24, "line_end": 24, "verbatim": "**Row 3:** Subject 003 was a screen failure, so they were not assigned to an arm or treated. The arm actual arm variables are null, and ARMNRS=\"SCREEN FAILURE\".", "parent_section": "§DM.2 [Example 2]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a016", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 26, "line_end": 26, "verbatim": "**Row 4:** Subject 004 withdrew during the run-in element. Like subject 003, they were not assigned to an arm or treated. However, they were not considered a screen failure, and ARMNRS=\"NOT ASSIGNED\".", "parent_section": "§DM.2 [Example 2]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a017", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 28, "line_end": 28, "verbatim": "**Row 5:** Subject 005 was randomized but dropped out before being treated. Thus, the actual arm variables are not populated and ARMNRS=\"ASSIGNED, NOT TREATED\".", "parent_section": "§DM.2 [Example 2]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
