{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a067", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 105, "line_end": 105, "verbatim": "The CRF in this example is annotated to show the CDASH variable name and the target SDTMIG variable. Data that are collected using the same variable name as defined in the SDTMIG are in RED. If the CDASHIG variable differs from the one defined in the SDTMIG, the CDASHIG variable is in GREY.", "parent_section": "§DM.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a068", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 107, "line_end": 107, "verbatim": "See the CDASH Model and Implementation Guide for additional information: https://www.cdisc.org/standards/foundational/cdash.", "parent_section": "§DM.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
