{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a081", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 160, "line_end": 160, "verbatim": "If the study participant answered AMERICAN INDIAN OR ALASKA NATIVE, subcategories (CRACE01-CRACE04) from the RACEC codelist are presented: ALASKA NATIVE, AMERICAN INDIAN, CARIBBEAN INDIAN, CENTRAL AMERICAN INDIAN.", "parent_section": "§DM.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a082", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 162, "line_end": 162, "verbatim": "If the study participant answered ASIAN, subcategories (CRACE05-CRACE10) are presented: ASIAN AMERICAN, ASIAN INDIAN, BANGLADESHI, CHINESE, JAPANESE, KOREAN.", "parent_section": "§DM.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a083", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 164, "line_end": 164, "verbatim": "If the study participant answered BLACK OR AFRICAN AMERICAN, subcategories (CRACE11-CRACE17) are presented: AFRICAN, AFRICAN AMERICAN, AFRICAN CARIBBEAN, BAHAMIAN, BARBADIAN, BLACK, BLACK CENTRAL AMERICAN.", "parent_section": "§DM.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a084", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 166, "line_end": 166, "verbatim": "If the study participant answered WHITE, subcategories (CRACE18-CRACE21) are presented: ARAB, EUROPEAN, MIDDLE EASTERN, RUSSIAN.", "parent_section": "§DM.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
