{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a107", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 200, "line_end": 200, "verbatim": "When a subject selects multiple race values, as USUBJID ABC789-010-047 did, the values selected are represented in SUPPDM. Collected race, which is the specific race subcategory (or subcategories) selected by each subject, is represented in SUPPDM to ensure subject self-identification and/or country-specific requirements are available for reference. CDASH recommended QNAM-QLABEL values have been provided.", "parent_section": "§DM.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a108", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 202, "line_end": 202, "verbatim": "**Rows 1, 2:** Show that USUBJID ABC789-010-047 selected 2 RACE values, \"ASIAN\" and \"WHITE\". CDASH recommended QNAM-QLABEL values have been provided.", "parent_section": "§DM.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmDM_ex_a109", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/DM/examples.md", "line_start": 204, "line_end": 204, "verbatim": "**Rows 3-5:** Show that USUBJID ABC789-010-047 selected 3 collected race (CRACE) values, \"CHINESE\", \"KOREAN\", and \"RUSSIAN\". CDASH recommended QNAM-QLABEL values have been provided.", "parent_section": "§DM.4 [Example 4]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T03:30:00Z"}}
